          "_name": "content6",
          "_sourceTheme": "churchm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"content6 churchm5\" group=\"Content\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Box\" name=\"showBox\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Border Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"border\" condition=\"showBox\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Container BG\" value=\"#E0AE8A\" name=\"container\" selected>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Image\" name=\"showImage\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffeec7\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.3\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverseContent}\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-1 card\">\n                <div class=\"box-wrapper\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-box mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-box\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showBox\">\n                        <b>WBC</b>\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-7 card\">\n                <div class=\"title-wrapper\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">We welcome you to Widefield Baptist Mission, located in Jones Ranch, New Mexico which is part of the Chichiltah Community. Established in the 1950's and part of the Baptist Mid-Mission, we are committed to biblical preaching, fervent prayer, and loving our neighbors.&nbsp; Whether you are from here, or from anywhere else, you are family here with us.<br><br>John 3:16<br>\"Háálá Diyin God éí nihokáá' dine'é t'áá íiyisí ayóó'ájó'níigo bąą haYe' t'ááłá'í há yizhchínígíí baazhníłtį́, áko t'áá háiida boodlą́ągo baa dzólíhígíí éí doo ádoodįįł da, nidi iiná doo ninít'i'ii bee hólǫ́ǫ dooleeł.\"<br><br></p>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\"><a class=\"btn btn-warning-outline\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                            <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-arrow-next mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                            START NOW!\n                        </a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-4 card\">\n                <div class=\"image-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n                    <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/00920easter20sunrise20service20around20the20campfire-1224x918.webp\" alt=\"Easter Sunrise around Campfire\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
